@casas_seguridad
title: Las casas de seguridad
subtitle: Rebuild the housing net: new doors, new names, the file's addresses gone stale in one season.
card-image: img/cards/urbana.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
on-arrival: advisor_action_timer = 6; last_advisor_action = 1; expediente -= 7; pres_valle += 2

She does it the way she does everything: completely, and in silence. Every lease ends, every key changes, every neighbor who noticed anything finds the noticing has moved away. The DFS's city map — years of patient watching, thousands of man-hours of parked cars — becomes, in one season, a museum of former addresses. Somewhere in Bucareli a major must explain the sudden blindness to a general, and cannot.

@imprenta_clandestina
title: La imprenta clandestina
subtitle: The war argues in print: communiqués that arrive folded inside the sports section.
card-image: img/cards/urbana.jpg
choose-if: advisor_action_timer == 0
unavailable-subtitle: [? if advisor_action_timer > 0 : [+ advisor_action_timer +] months before next advisor action. ?]
